Package com.chillycheesy.modulo.commands.operator.builder

Class OperatorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chillycheesy.modulo.commands.operator.builder.OperatorBuilder
  • public class OperatorBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to build an Operator form any Object. The Object can have the following annotations:
    • Operator
    • OperatorFindByRegex
    The Object can implement the following interfaces:
    • OperatorListener
    • OperatorFinder
